This repository is a throughline *source*: a requirements graph, not a program. It
re-expresses the UK Government Digital Service (GDS) Service Standard as a grounded
IDD graph so consuming projects can compose it with throughline-compose.

The GDS Service Standard is published by the UK Government on GOV.UK and is Crown
